latestPosts.caption:
The Queen ruling our Sparkly Bitch top!🔥🪩🖤

@deepikapadukone featured in @hellomagindia 🧿💣

Posted @withrepost • @hellomagindia #HELLOCover: The reigning queen of the industry, #DeepikaPadukone (@deepikapadukone), graces the cover of our November issue as she scripts a new chapter in global domination with the launch of her self-care brand @82e.official.
.
Alongside gaining global ground, the actor’s style evolution has been unparalleled, and she carries every ensemble with ease. Here, she wears an embellished Miakee (@miakee.official) mesh top and an H&M (@hm) bralette. She completes the look with Cartier’s (@cartier) Juste un Clou bracelets, a Diamond Paved Love bracelet, a Juste un Clou ring, Clash de Cartier ring and an Ecrou de Cartier ring.
.
Grab your copy of this month's issue to unfold a new chapter of Padukone's life and much more.
.

I’ve always loved shopping from H&M and Zara, but sometimes their collections didn’t quite hit the mark for me-either the styles didn’t feel fresh or I couldn’t find exactly what I was looking for. So, I’ve been on the lookout for a brand that offers more variety and unique options, and I finally found it @miakee.official ! 💖

Their collection has the perfect mix of trendy and timeless, with dresses that feel effortlessly chic and so versatile for every occasion. Whether it’s a brunch date, a casual day out, or even an evening event @miakee.official has something that fits the vibe perfectly.
